      "name": "Motion Design",
      "abstract": "Motion design connects visual culture, interface semantics, typography, animation, sound, choreography and web interaction.",
      "description": "Motion design is the use of time, movement, transition, rhythm and sequencing to structure visual communication and interface behavior.",
